{"about_the_game":"<strong>Midnight Arrow</strong> is an atmospheric puzzle platformer that uses a retro art style. <strong>Hop</strong> on platforms and <strong>jump</strong> on walls to <strong>explore</strong> a <strong>vast immersive platforming world</strong>. <strong>Discove</strong> the different types of arrows and use them to <strong>solve puzzles</strong> and <strong>illuminate</strong> the darkened world around you! Oh and did I mention you can now create your own levels? \ud83d\udc40<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/iceBlue.gif?t=1720082471\" /><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tight smooth platforming \ud83e\udd98<br></li><li>Optional quests \ud83c\udfc6<br></li><li>Collectables \ud83c\udf6d<br></li><li>Skins \ud83d\udc55<br></li><li>6 areas with new mechanics \ud83c\udfd4\ufe0f<br></li><li>New Puzzles in every area \ud83e\udde9<br></li><li>Level Editor \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f<br></li><li>Speedrunning Stuff \u23f0</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Light up your path</strong> </h2>through the dark caverns using fire arrows.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/gif2.gif?t=1720082471\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Solve puzzles</strong> </h2>than test your aim, platforming, and dexterity abilities, all at the same time. You need to do both puzzle-solving and platforming at the same time and if you are extra good at platforming you can even cheese the game for some speedrunning advantage! \ud83e\uddc0<br>Each area brings new mechanics that add to the complexity of the platforming and the challenges of the puzzles. The game has a total of 6 areas each with its unique mood and playstyle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2310670/extras/gif3.gif?t=1720082471\" /><h2 class=\"bb_ta